          <h2 class="display-font text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-secondary leading-tight">The work we run every week.</h2>
          <p class="text-neutral-dark-gray text-lg max-w-3xl">
            From one-day fixes to full remodels, our crews show up with a clear scope, tidy sites, and a single point of contact.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-light-gray bg-white px-4 py-4 shadow-sm space-y-2">
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-mid">What you can expect</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-neutral-light px-3 py-1 text-sm text-neutral-dark">
              <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>Permits + inspections
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-neutral-light px-3 py-1 text-sm text-neutral-dark">
              <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>Jobsite protection
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-neutral-light px-3 py-1 text-sm text-neutral-dark">
              <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>Transparent pricing
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-light-gray bg-white p-6 shadow-sm hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md transition">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary uppercase tracking-[0.14em]">Repairs</p>
            <span class="text-2xl">üõ†Ô∏è</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="display-font text-xl font-semibold text-secondary mb-2">Repairs & punch</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-dark-gray leading-relaxed">Cabinetry, drywall, hardware, and finish fixes that keep your space in top shape.</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1.5 text-sm text-neutral-dark-gray">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>Doors, trim, and drywall</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>Fixture swaps and lighting</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>Touch-ups and punch completion</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-light-gray bg-white p-6 shadow-sm hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md transition">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary uppercase tracking-[0.14em]">Remodels</p>
            <span class="text-2xl">üè°</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="display-font text-xl font-semibold text-secondary mb-2">Remodels & additions</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-dark-gray leading-relaxed">Kitchen, bath, and whole-home work with dust control and milestone updates.</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1.5 text-sm text-neutral-dark-gray">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>Design-build collaboration</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>Structural + MEP coordination</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>Permits handled in-house</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-light-gray bg-white p-6 shadow-sm hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-md transition">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary uppercase tracking-[0.14em]">Commercial</p>
            <span class="text-2xl">üè¢</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="display-font text-xl font-semibold text-secondary mb-2">Commercial upkeep</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-dark-gray leading-relaxed">Phased work plans that keep tenants and teams productive while we upgrade your space.</p>
          <ul class="mt-3 space-y-1.5 text-sm text-neutral-dark-gray">
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>Office, retail, hospitality</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>Night + weekend crews</li>
            <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>Preventive maintenance plans</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-secondary text-neutral-light">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 space-y-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-6">
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent">Process</p>
            <h2 class="display-font text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-neutral-white leading-tight">A steady, four-step rhythm.</h2>
            <p class="text-neutral-light-gray text-lg max-w-2xl">
              Clear steps keep projects moving: we map the work, lock budget and schedule, build with daily updates, then close out fast.
            </p>
          </div>
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-white/30 px-5 py-3 text-neutral-white font-semibold hover:bg-white/10 transition"
          >
            Schedule a walkthrough
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-4">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5">
            <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-primary/20 text-neutral-white font-semibold flex items-center justify-center mb-3">01</div>
            <p class="display-font text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-white mb-1">Site walk</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-light-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">Document conditions, risks, and quick wins. You get a scope that fits real-world constraints.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5">
            <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-accent/30 text-neutral-dark font-semibold flex items-center justify-center mb-3">02</div>
            <p class="display-font text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-white mb-1">Plan + budget</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-light-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">Transparent pricing, alternates where they help, and a schedule you can track.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5">
            <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-neutral-light/20 text-neutral-white font-semibold flex items-center justify-center mb-3">03</div>
            <p class="display-font text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-white mb-1">Build + update</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-light-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">Dedicated lead on-site, photo reports, and tidy protection for occupied spaces.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-neutral-white/5 border border-white/10 p-5">
            <div class="h-10 w-10 rounded-full bg-primary/20 text-neutral-white font-semibold flex items-center justify-center mb-3">04</div>
            <p class="display-font text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-white mb-1">Close out</p>
            <p class="text-neutral-light-gray text-sm leading-relaxed">Punch resolved quickly, warranties issued, and a walkthrough to confirm every detail.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-[1.05fr,0.95fr] gap-10 items-center">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary">Why it works</p>
        <h3 class="display-font text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold text-secondary leading-tight">Built for busy homeowners and teams.</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-dark-gray text-lg leading-relaxed">
          You get one accountable lead, vetted trades, and a clean site. We communicate daily so you never wonder what‚Äôs happening on the job.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3">
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-light-gray bg-white px-4 py-4 shadow-sm">
            <p class="display-font text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary">4.9‚òÖ</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-mid">Client rating across projects</p>
          </div>
          <div class="rounded-2xl border border-neutral-light-gray bg-white px-4 py-4 shadow-sm">
            <p class="display-font text-2xl font-semibold text-secondary">72 hrs</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-neutral-mid">Site visits available</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white border border-neutral-light-gray shadow-md p-6 space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <div>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-primary">In-field notes</p>
            <p class="display-font text-xl font-semibold text-secondary">How we keep flow</p>
          </div>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-neutral-light px-3 py-1 text-sm text-neutral-dark">
            <span class="h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>Real updates
          </span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-dark-gray">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
            <span>Daily check-ins with photos for remote owners and property managers.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
            <span>Material tracking and delivery windows planned before demo begins.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="mt-1 h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-primary"></span>
            <span>Clean protection and ventilation plans so occupied spaces stay livable.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-6 mb-12">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white border border-neutral-light-gray rounded-3xl shadow-lg px-6 md:px-10 py-10 flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-center md:justify-between gap-6">
        <div class="space-y-2">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary">Ready to start?</p>
          <h3 class="display-font text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-secondary">Let‚Äôs map your scope and schedule.</h3>
          <p class="text-neutral-dark-gray text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
            Share a quick note about your project and we‚Äôll return a tidy plan with budget, timeline, and next steps.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 w-full md:w-auto">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 bg-primary text-neutral-white font-semibold px-5 py-3 rounded-xl shadow-md hover:bg-primary-dark transition"
          >
            Book a consult
            <span aria-hidden="true">‚Üí</span>
          </a>
          <a
            href="tel:+14157678986"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-secondary/20 px-5 py-3 text-secondary font-semibold hover:border-secondary/50 transition"
          >
            Call 415-767-8986
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
